snippet.title: Project 06 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Take a peek at Wave Ocean and how the game has progressed in this little teaser for P-06.
Happy 2019 everybody!

The footage of this teaser has been recorded in a slightly old build of P-06, and the project as of now has evolved even more than what you see here.

btw this is not gistix or mefiresu, this is ChaosX!

Footage by BeatZ - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEjwges-3BTaWsMwOGJDoGQ
Editing and composition by ChaosX

pls subcribe :)
